EventItemTitle:
DESIGNATION OF MINORITY LEADER
We, the undersigned members of the Minority (Republican) Delegation of the Council of the City of New York, hereby designate and appoint Steven Matteo as Minority Leader of the New York City Council, pursuant to Rule 4.10 of the Rules of the Council of the City of New York for the remainder of the term that commenced on January 1, 2014. Dated July 1, 2015. 
Signed: Vincent M. Ignizio and Steven Matteo
